## 4. How Agents Use This File

- On session start:
  - Read `tasks/lessons.md`.
  - Apply domain-specific rules when planning and implementing.
- When new lessons are added:
  - They become rules for future sessions.
  - Agents should avoid repeating the same mistake category.
